urlLink ERIC Digest Blog   This blog is trying to keep ERIC Digests in the forefront now that the ERIC Clearinghouse system is dead.   It blogs a different digest each day.  With over 2800+ ERIC Digests, this means that blog will have over 8 years of life.  :]  From the site:  This blog features the different education ERIC Digests created by the ERIC Clearinghouse system. These clearinghouses are now gone but this blog will highlight the various ERIC Digests. These digests were well done and they deserve the continued attention of parents and educators.